INSERT INTO feedback_entries (id, task_id, discovery_item_id, feedback_type, content, summary, source_execution_id)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
            RETURNING
                id as "id!: Uuid",
                task_id as "task_id: Uuid",
                discovery_item_id as "discovery_item_id: Uuid",
                feedback_type as "feedback_type!: FeedbackType",
                content,
                summary,
                source_execution_id as "source_execution_id: Uuid",
                created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
